Formerly,Skynet,Meshblu,is,an,API,for,the,internet,of,things,With,a,collaborative,approach,Skynet,offers,an,API,that,helps,developers,to,make,drones,dance,turn,on,hue,light,bulbs,and,control,electronic,devices,like,Belkin,WeMo,This,hybrid,cloud,API,also,offers,to,send,and,receive,messages,to,and,from,devices,to,monitor,sensor,activities,The,main,value,of,Skynet,is,a,chrome,app,already,built,in,the,market,named,NodeBlu,This,app,helps,developers,to,experiment,with,easy,dragging,dropping,and,writing,in,their,own,terms,Some,of,the,features,of,this,API,include,status,devices,messages,events,and,data,The,site,provides,examples,in,REST,a,demo,and,social,media,for,additional,support